  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The real estate men are boosting\nthe booster spirit in earnest, and at\na meeting last night decided to\nraise publicity fund of $4,000 to\nhe used in exploiting Spokane. The\nmeeting was held at the Masonic\ntemple and was presided over by\nD. NJ. Thompson. The plan agreed\nupon is to have a committee make\nassessments on the $50 different\nfirms, the assessments to be pay\nable monthly and to be graded &C\ncording to the ability Of the firms to\npay specified amounts.\n\n\n4 An effort was made to start the\nsubscriptions last night and several\nlarge offers were rendered, but it\nwas thought best to wait until the\ncommittee was ready to act. The\nmatter will come up again in two\nweeks, when a second meeting will\nbe held."
    }
  ]
